  <brief_title>The Latarjet-type Procedure Using the SEM Positioner: Using a Scan to Assess Consolidation</brief_title>
  <acronym>IACE Scan</acronym>
  <official_title>Treatment of Chronic Anterior Shoulder Instability by a Latarjet-type Bone Block Procedure Using the SEM (Science Et Medecine) Positioning Tool: Using a Scan to Assess Consolidation and Return to Normal Activity at 3 Months</official_title>
  <sponsors>
